\c 18
\p
\v 1 Anozviparadzanisa anongotsvaka chishuvo; anopazira uchenjeri hwakanaka hwose.
\p
\v 2 Benzi harifari mukunzwisisa, asi kuti moyo waro ufukurwe.
\p
\v 3 Kana wakaipa achiuya, kuzvidza kunouyawo; pamwe chete nezvinonyadzisa, kushora \add kunouya\add*wo.
\p
\v 4 Mashoko emuromo wemunhu imvura yakadzika; chitubu chenjere rukova rwunoyerera.
\p
\v 5 Hazvina kunaka kugamuchira chiso chewakaipa, kutsausa wakarurama pamutongo.
\p
\v 6 Miromo yebenzi inopinda pagakava; nemuromo waro unodana shamhu zhinji.
\p
\v 7 Muromo webenzi kuparadzwa kwaro; uye miromo yaro musungo wemweya waro.
\p
\v 8 Mashoko emucheri akaita semisuva inomedzwa nekukurumidza; iyo ndoburukira mukati-kati medumbu.
\p
\v 9 Neari simbe pabasa rake, iye munin'ina wenyanzvi yeuparadzi.
\p
\v 10 Zita raJehovha ishongwe yakasimba; wakarurama achamhanyira kwairi agomiswa akachengeteka.
\p
\v 11 Fuma yemufumi iguta rake rakasimba, uye serusvingo rurefu pakufunga kwake.
\p
\v 12 Moyo wemunhu anozvikudza kuparadzwa kusati kwava\add po\add*; uye kuzvininipisa kunotangira rukudzo.
\p
\v 13 Anopindura nyaya asati anzwa, upenzi nechinyadzo kwaari.
\p
\v 14 Mweya wemunhu uchatsigira kurwara kwake; asi ndiani angatakura mweya wakaputsika?
\p
\v 15 Moyo weanonzwisisa unowana ruzivo; uye nzeve yewakachenjera inotsvaka ruzivo.
\p
\v 16 Chipo chemunhu chinomuzaririra pakafaranuka, uye chinomutungamirira pamberi pevakuru.
\p
\v 17 Anotanga pamhosva yake \add anoonekwa\add* akarurama; asi wekwake anosvika ndokumuferefeta.
\p
\v 18 Mujenya unopedza magakava, uye unoparadzanisa pakati pevane simba.
\p
\v 19 Hama yatadzirwa inopfuura guta rakasimba; uye makakava akaita sechipfigiso cheimba yamambo.
\p
\v 20 Dumbu remunhu rinogutswa nezvibereko zvemuromo wake; achaguta nezvinowanikwa zvemiromo yake.
\p
\v 21 Rufu neupenyu zviri muruoko rwerurimi; uye vanoruda vachadya chibereko charwo.
\p
\v 22 Wawana mukadzi wawana chakanaka, uye wagamuchira nyasha kuna Jehovha.
\p
\v 23 Murombo anotaura mikumbiro, asi mufumi anopindura zvinhu zvehasha.
\p
\v 24 Munhu ane shamwari zhinji achaparara; asi kune mudikanwi anonamatira kupfuura hama.